In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla. Stir in KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal and coconut until well coated. Shape mixture into sixteen 7 cm nests. Fill cooled nests with miniature marshmallows, jelly beans, or chocolate eggs. Best if served same day.